            <title>[FLINK-19535] SourceCoordinator should avoid fail job multiple times.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-19535</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently the &lt;tt&gt;SourceCoordinator&lt;/tt&gt; may invoke &lt;tt&gt;SourceCoordinatorContext#failJob()&lt;/tt&gt; multiple times from the same instance. This may cause the job to failover multiple times unnecessarily. The &lt;tt&gt;SourceCoordinator&lt;/tt&gt; should instead just fail the job once.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
